1
00:00:42,400 --> 00:00:43,800
Judging solely from the case file,

2
00:00:43,800 --> 00:00:45,400
the Qin Shitou case indeed has no loopholes.

3
00:00:46,440 --> 00:00:48,280
But they forgot the most important point.

4
00:00:49,240 --> 00:00:49,920
What is it?

5
00:00:50,720 --> 00:00:52,360
Li Niangu lives in the East Market,

6
00:00:52,800 --> 00:00:54,320
so it should be under the jurisdiction of Wannian County.

7
00:00:55,520 --> 00:00:56,560
But why was this case

8
00:00:56,840 --> 00:00:58,160
judged by Chang'an County?

9
00:01:00,080 --> 00:01:00,800
I remember now.

10
00:01:01,360 --> 00:01:02,960
Before Li Niangu became Vice Director of the Ministry of Revenue,

11
00:01:03,360 --> 00:01:04,440
he was the Deputy County Magistrate of Chang'an County.

12
00:01:07,160 --> 00:01:07,800
Lady Xiaomu,

13
00:01:08,640 --> 00:01:11,440
please go to the Wannian County forage yard to check the accounts.

14
00:01:12,160 --> 00:01:12,880
Go now.

15
00:01:13,560 --> 00:01:14,040
Okay.

16
00:01:16,440 --> 00:01:16,840
Lao Yao,

17
00:01:17,000 --> 00:01:17,520
let's go.

18
00:01:20,720 --> 00:01:21,880
Say, Shentu,

19
00:01:22,080 --> 00:01:23,720
you're getting quite comfortable using my people.

20
00:01:24,080 --> 00:01:25,120
Isn't that for your sake?

21
00:01:26,160 --> 00:01:26,960
I like the sound of that.

22
00:01:27,400 --> 00:01:27,880
Let's go.

23
00:01:28,000 --> 00:01:28,880
We're going to Qin Shitou's house.

24
00:01:29,160 --> 00:01:29,560
Let's go.

25
00:01:55,400 --> 00:01:55,800
Lao Yao.

26
00:01:56,080 --> 00:01:56,480
Hmm.

27
00:01:57,040 --> 00:01:58,360
Look at all this dust in the room.

28
00:01:58,720 --> 00:01:59,600
Did you find anything?

29
00:02:00,080 --> 00:02:00,640
Stop keeping me in suspense.

30
00:02:00,920 --> 00:02:01,400
Just say it.

31
00:02:01,880 --> 00:02:03,680
It proves that this Headless Ghost Reanimation Case

32
00:02:04,080 --> 00:02:05,640
is just smoke and mirrors.

33
00:02:06,800 --> 00:02:07,520
Why?

34
00:02:08,440 --> 00:02:09,080
Why?

35
00:02:10,400 --> 00:02:11,800
If you became a walking corpse,

36
00:02:11,800 --> 00:02:12,800
wouldn't you come home to take a look?

37
00:02:14,000 --> 00:02:14,880
You're the walking corpse!

38
00:02:15,280 --> 00:02:16,280
Can't you say something nice?

39
00:02:16,440 --> 00:02:17,120
Just kidding.

40
00:02:19,680 --> 00:02:20,480
However,

41
00:02:20,680 --> 00:02:22,080
if, as Li Niangu said,

42
00:02:22,480 --> 00:02:23,600
Qin Shitou was convicted

43
00:02:24,040 --> 00:02:25,200
and his wife left...

44
00:02:26,000 --> 00:02:27,440
even if she left in a hurry,

45
00:02:27,440 --> 00:02:30,520
the room wouldn't be this messy.

46
00:02:31,200 --> 00:02:32,920
It looks like it was ransacked.

47
00:02:34,280 --> 00:02:35,280
This doesn't make sense.

48
00:02:42,720 --> 00:02:43,920
Of course it doesn't make sense.

49
00:02:44,200 --> 00:02:46,160
Because she never left Chang'an City.

50
00:02:48,520 --> 00:02:49,640
This is an infant's diaper.

51
00:02:50,240 --> 00:02:51,520
The Qin family has a pair of infants.

52
00:02:51,840 --> 00:02:52,720
As a mother,

53
00:02:53,200 --> 00:02:54,240
even if she left something behind,

54
00:02:54,480 --> 00:02:55,360
she wouldn't leave this behind.

55
00:02:56,160 --> 00:02:57,480
Then if she didn't leave,

56
00:02:57,800 --> 00:02:58,720
where did she go?

57
00:03:00,080 --> 00:03:00,280
Who?

58
00:03:02,680 --> 00:03:03,080
Who is it?

59
00:03:06,480 --> 00:03:07,720
It seems someone is watching this place.

60
00:03:11,040 --> 00:03:12,240
An empty house,

61
00:03:12,880 --> 00:03:14,000
yet someone is watching it.

62
00:03:14,800 --> 00:03:16,800
It means there's something in this house that he wants.

63
00:03:19,280 --> 00:03:19,960
What does he want?

64
00:03:21,000 --> 00:03:22,000
We'll just give it to him.

65
00:03:24,600 --> 00:03:26,000
Do you have another scheme in mind?

66
00:03:43,360 --> 00:03:43,800
Shentu

67
00:03:44,360 --> 00:03:44,880
Impressive.

68
00:03:45,680 --> 00:03:46,640
Your guess was spot on.

69
00:03:48,320 --> 00:03:48,760
My Lord.

70
00:03:54,520 --> 00:03:54,800
My Lord.

71
00:03:55,160 --> 00:03:55,520
Master.

72
00:03:55,520 --> 00:03:56,080
Mm-hmm.

73
00:03:56,600 --> 00:03:57,960
We've investigated the accounts of the Forage yard.

74
00:03:58,400 --> 00:04:00,120
Qin Shitou indeed did not embezzle the forage money.

75
00:04:00,600 --> 00:04:01,440
He was framed.

76
00:04:02,920 --> 00:04:05,200
What did Li Niangu want from Qin Shitou?

77
00:04:06,040 --> 00:04:07,200
To make an official like him

78
00:04:07,760 --> 00:04:08,840
go to such great lengths?

79
00:04:09,360 --> 00:04:10,880
His pair of boy-girl twins.

80
00:04:14,320 --> 00:04:15,480
There is a vicious dark art

81
00:04:16,000 --> 00:04:16,680
called Human Foundation Sacrifice.

82
00:04:17,480 --> 00:04:19,360
Sealing a boy and a girl in a coffin with wax,

83
00:04:19,920 --> 00:04:20,840
and burying them before the house or behind the courtyard

84
00:04:21,440 --> 00:04:22,040
to pray for great fortune.

85
00:04:23,320 --> 00:04:24,120
How cruel.

86
00:04:25,080 --> 00:04:26,400
That day when we went to the Li residence,

87
00:04:26,480 --> 00:04:28,000
I mentioned the Qin family members.

88
00:04:28,960 --> 00:04:30,160
Li Niangu involuntarily

89
00:04:30,160 --> 00:04:31,960
glanced at that stone under the tree in the courtyard.

90
00:04:32,360 --> 00:04:33,280
On that stone,

91
00:04:33,880 --> 00:04:34,640
a tiger was carved.

92
00:04:37,840 --> 00:04:38,480
Rumor has it that

93
00:04:38,720 --> 00:04:40,080
tigers can devour ghosts and demons,

94
00:04:40,800 --> 00:04:41,600
and are used to guard tombs.

95
00:04:42,360 --> 00:04:43,160
I was wondering at the time

96
00:04:43,480 --> 00:04:44,640
why there would be a tiger there.

97
00:04:45,000 --> 00:04:45,680
Now it seems

98
00:04:46,440 --> 00:04:47,400
it was all for the Human Foundation Sacrifice.

99
00:04:49,360 --> 00:04:51,960
But what is the relationship between Liu Mu and Qin Shitou?

100
00:04:52,240 --> 00:04:53,120
That he would take revenge for him?

101
00:04:53,600 --> 00:04:54,720
Even if they were close,

102
00:04:55,640 --> 00:04:56,960
he wouldn't go this far.

103
00:04:57,480 --> 00:04:59,600
Liu Mu and Qin Shitou share a similar past.

104
00:05:00,800 --> 00:05:01,760
That is why he used

105
00:05:01,760 --> 00:05:03,600
the guise of Qin Shitou to play the walking corpse,

106
00:05:04,320 --> 00:05:05,360
wanting to make Li Niangu taste

107
00:05:05,880 --> 00:05:06,720
the flavor of fear.

108
00:05:12,280 --> 00:05:13,560
If I were Liu Mu,

109
00:05:14,760 --> 00:05:15,840
where would I be?

110
00:05:56,440 --> 00:05:56,960
It wasn't me!

111
00:05:58,120 --> 00:05:58,760
I didn't do it!

112
00:05:59,520 --> 00:06:01,080
Li Niangu forced me to do it!

113
00:06:04,200 --> 00:06:04,640
Let me go!

114
00:06:05,240 --> 00:06:06,040
Let me go!

115
00:06:07,560 --> 00:06:08,480
Human Foundation Sacrifice...

116
00:06:10,520 --> 00:06:11,720
is done by sealing with wax, right?

117
00:06:14,440 --> 00:06:15,080
Spare my life!

118
00:06:15,680 --> 00:06:16,280
Spare my life!

119
00:06:16,800 --> 00:06:18,400
The boy from half a year ago,

120
00:06:19,400 --> 00:06:21,480
did you ever think of sparing his life?

121
00:06:22,280 --> 00:06:23,200
You are not Qin Shitou.

122
00:06:25,040 --> 00:06:25,640
Who exactly are you?

123
00:06:38,680 --> 00:06:40,280
Half a year ago, my little brother

124
00:06:41,080 --> 00:06:42,920
was tortured by you like this too, wasn't he?

125
00:06:43,560 --> 00:06:47,040
His heart must have been as full of fear as yours is now.

126
00:07:00,040 --> 00:07:00,440
Liu Mu!

127
00:07:05,680 --> 00:07:07,640
Go down there and keep my little brother company!

128
00:07:11,680 --> 00:07:12,320
You evil ghost!

129
00:07:14,600 --> 00:07:15,040
Jerk!

130
00:07:15,880 --> 00:07:16,360
Go to hell!

131
00:07:17,200 --> 00:07:18,000
Die!

132
00:07:23,360 --> 00:07:25,880
He is extremely familiar with the Hongxiu crime scene.

133
00:07:25,960 --> 00:07:26,360
Search separately.

134
00:07:26,520 --> 00:07:26,640
Yes, sir.

135
00:07:26,840 --> 00:07:27,640
He can't be far from it.

136
00:07:28,800 --> 00:07:30,080
Changsheng Fang.

137
00:07:39,720 --> 00:07:41,520
Liu Mu relied on his skill in Huaiyang Cuisine

138
00:07:41,520 --> 00:07:42,720
to get into the Li residence.

139
00:07:43,040 --> 00:07:45,000
Since he needs to practice cooking often,

140
00:07:45,040 --> 00:07:47,840
his residence must be adjacent to the Marketplace.

141
00:07:52,080 --> 00:07:53,280
Since he cooks Huaiyang Cuisine,

142
00:07:53,400 --> 00:07:54,800
he must find people from Huaiyang to taste his dishes

143
00:07:55,160 --> 00:07:56,400
so he can make a name for himself

144
00:07:56,560 --> 00:07:57,560
and be discovered by Li Niangu.

145
00:07:58,520 --> 00:07:58,800
Therefore,

146
00:08:02,600 --> 00:08:05,200
the Huaiyang shops on both sides of the street.

147
00:09:00,120 --> 00:09:00,520
Lord Li

148
00:09:01,000 --> 00:09:02,200
told us to dump the body outside the city.

149
00:09:02,560 --> 00:09:02,760
Hurry.

150
00:09:03,320 --> 00:09:03,880
Let me catch my breath.

151
00:09:04,000 --> 00:09:04,600
Stop dawdling.

152
00:09:05,080 --> 00:09:05,280
Wait.

153
00:09:05,880 --> 00:09:06,320
What's that sound?

154
00:09:06,840 --> 00:09:08,440
Th-th-the b-b-box... inside the box!

155
00:09:10,280 --> 00:09:10,480
This...

156
00:09:11,120 --> 00:09:11,840
It's a walking corpse!

157
00:09:38,880 --> 00:09:39,360
Ghost!

158
00:09:40,280 --> 00:09:40,840
Ghost!

159
00:09:42,520 --> 00:09:42,800
Ghost!

160
00:09:44,680 --> 00:09:45,000
It wasn't me!

161
00:09:45,520 --> 00:09:46,000
It wasn't me!

162
00:10:34,960 --> 00:10:36,720
Give me the ball.

163
00:10:37,240 --> 00:10:39,280
Give me the ball.

164
00:10:39,640 --> 00:10:42,080
Give me the ball.

165
00:10:57,240 --> 00:10:57,760
Don't haunt me.

166
00:10:58,280 --> 00:10:58,920
I've become a high official.

167
00:10:59,200 --> 00:10:59,840
I'll make you proper offerings.

168
00:11:00,040 --> 00:11:00,880
I'll make you all proper offerings.

169
00:11:01,400 --> 00:11:01,840
Don't haunt me.

170
00:11:02,240 --> 00:11:03,040
Don't haunt me.

171
00:11:17,560 --> 00:11:18,880
Mother.

172
00:11:22,080 --> 00:11:23,680
Mother.

173
00:11:25,320 --> 00:11:26,480
Mother.

174
00:11:27,600 --> 00:11:28,760
Mother.

175
00:11:31,160 --> 00:11:32,320
No one will come here again.

176
00:11:33,240 --> 00:11:33,880
Bury her in the courtyard.

177
00:11:34,120 --> 00:11:34,800
Mother.

178
00:11:41,280 --> 00:11:43,040
I swear you'll pay with blood.
